msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Wenn du jenois us de US bist, empfehlen mir NOWPayments (niedrigste "
"Gebühren, direkt zu deinem Wallet). Wenn du im US bist, is Stripe Crypto au "
"e Option. Du kannst meh Services aktivieren und deine Besucher wähle los!"

